<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <style>
        .welcome-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .welcome-message {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .start-button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .start-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="welcome-container">
        <h1>Welcome, <%= username %>!</h1>
        
        <div class="welcome-message">
            <p>Thank you for joining us! To help us provide you with the best recommendations, 
            we need to know a little more about you.</p>
            <p>We'll ask you a few quick questions about your qualifications, skills, and interests.</p>
        </div>

        <button class="start-button" onclick="window.location.href='/questions/<%= userId %>'">
            Get Started
        </button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>